    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014it\u2019s in stunning, like-new condition and has been pampered since day one. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh car smell! Seriously, it's a total gem. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
